-1 LEVEL~
Syntax: level or exp
This provides a detailed synopsis of important aspects of your character.
Weapon skills, Magic skill and Stances are all shown.

Weapon skills have a maximum of 200 unless your a highlander when it
becomes 1000. Werewolves have a maximum unarmed of 400.

Stances have a maximum of 200.

