-1 IMMORTAL IMMORTALS~
Immortals are characters who don't play the game. Instead its an immortals
job to build and improve the mud. If an Immortal is on they
are listed under the 'Member of Staff' section of who. They are often
helpful and will answer most questions you may have about the game.

Immortals are also commonly referred to as Wizzes, Gods, Implementors,
Coders, Builders, Admin etc.
~
