The Wendigo are an ancient tribe much like the Native Americans. The Wendigo
fight to protect their dwindling lands. Their gifts are of the frozen north,
and their totem the Great Wendigo.

The Gifts of the Wendigo tribe are as follows:

#0[#7*#0]#n     Camouflage
         Syntax: camouflage <target>
         Garou with this gift are able to blend in with those around them.
         They are able to look like anyone.
	
#0[#7**#0]#n    Cutting Wind
        Syntax: cuttingwind <target>
        Garou with this gift may summon the bitter winds of the north.
        These winds will rip at a chosen foe.
	
#0[#7***#0]#n   Call the Cannibal Spirit
         Syntax: cannibal <target>
         With this gift Garou may summon a Great Wendigo avatar. This beast
         will hunt down the designated target.
	
#0[#7****#0]#n  Heart of Ice
         Syntax: heartofice <target>
         With this gift Garou may summon the frost of Wendigo to freeze an enemy.
	
#0[#7*****#0]#n Chill of the Early Frost
         Syntax: chill
         With this gift a Garou can call the very essence of the Great Wendigo.
         The area is blanketed with cold, the skys turn white.
#0-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-#n
~

