0 VOODOO~
Syntax: voodoo <victim> <action>

First, a doll of the victim is needed. There are three voodoo actions.  
The first, 'Stab', is only of use as a warning to the victim, or
to cause annoyance.  The second, 'Throw', will hurl the victim from their
feet and cause a small amount of damage.  The third and final action,
'Burn', will set the victim on fire, as well as destroy the doll itself.

~


