0 MASTERY~
#0-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-#n
Items of mastery are objects of great power. Players can create these
objects once they have reached 20000 hitpoints and Mastered ALL weapons,
